// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
// Antigravity v2 — Functions Error Test Suite
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
//
// This file serves as a manifest documenting the error test scripts
// located in the 'test_errors' directory.
//
// Each file intentionally triggers a specific compiler or runtime
// error. Run them individually to verify exit codes and error messages.
//
// 1. Calling with too few arguments (A2)
//    - File: test_errors/err_too_few_args.tiny
//    - Expected exit code: 70
//    - Expected output:
//      test_errors/err_too_few_args.tiny:6:6: Runtime error: Function 'greet' expects 2 to 3 argument(s) but got 1.
//      greet("John")
//           ^
//
// 2. Calling with too many arguments (A2)
//    - File: test_errors/err_too_many_args.tiny
//    - Expected exit code: 70
//    - Expected output:
//      test_errors/err_too_many_args.tiny:6:6: Runtime error: Function 'greet' expects 1 to 2 argument(s) but got 3.
//      greet("Ana", "Hi", "Extra")
//           ^
//
// 3. Calling a non-function value (A5)
//    - File: test_errors/err_not_callable.tiny
//    - Expected exit code: 70
//    - Expected output:
//      test_errors/err_not_callable.tiny:4:2: Runtime error: Cannot call a value of type 'integer'.
//      x()
//       ^
//
// 4. Calling an undefined name (A5)
//    - File: test_errors/err_undefined.tiny
//    - Expected exit code: 70
//    - Expected output:
//      test_errors/err_undefined.tiny:3:1: Semantic error: Undefined variable 'foo'.
//      foo()
//      ^
//
// 5. Recursion depth exceeded (A6)
//    - File: test_errors/err_max_recursion.tiny
//    - Expected exit code: 70
//    - Expected output:
//      test_errors/err_max_recursion.tiny:4:12: Runtime error: Maximum recursion depth exceeded (limit: 1000).
//          recurse()
//                 ^
//
// 6. Default parameter placed before a required one (A2)
//    - File: test_errors/err_invalid_defaults.tiny
//    - Expected exit code: 65
//    - Expected output:
//      test_errors/err_invalid_defaults.tiny:3:41: Parse error: at 'middle': Required parameter cannot follow default parameter.
//      define greet taking first be "John" and middle and last be "Smith"
//                                              ^

